body.name: Nightstand with Charging Station and LED Lights, Black Bedside Night Stands with 2 Drawers and Open Storage Shelves, Modern End Side Tables for Bedroom,Office
features: 【Led Nightstand With RGB Lights】This nightstand comes with Multi-Color RGB LED backlight, you can choose the light and mode according to needs and scenes. Over 60000 RGB lights, 29 dynamic modes, built-in mic, timing function, lights beat and flash in time with music, all controlled by a button or mobile APP. The beautiful LED lights will make your home looks more modern and fashionable.

【Nightstand With Charging Station】The bedside nightstand is arranged with 2 AC Outlets, 2 USB Ports, 1 on-off switch and a 4.9ft long power cable allowing you to charge mobile devices like cell phones, pads, lamps, laptops, etc. Easy to use within arm’s reach. And a USB Port is applied to connect the led light strip. This will reduce the clutter of charging wires and improve the convenience of your life.

【Nightstand With 2 Drawers】This 34in tall nightstand with 2 built-in drawers and easy-pull metal handle can go smoothly with the rails, providing enough space to organize your stuff and give you a neat space. The outstretched top shelf adds more storage space for small items. The open shelf is convenient for the daily use. Suitable for bedroom, living room, office play room.

【Durable and Sturdy】Made of P2 particleboard and rigid metal frame, this bed side table can hold up to 44lbs, and the drawer 11lbs. High quality waterproof surface treatment, easy to clean and maintain, durable. Modern aesthetic blends black with the frosted surface for added charm. It looks more beautiful with the colored lights in the dark and creates fantastic ambiance in your room.

【Easy to Assemble】This black nightstand with led lights can be a perfect gift for your friends or families. It can enrich bedroom space and as a nightlight to take the fear of dark nights away. Comes with step-by-step instructions and installation tools, you can finish assembly in short time. Feel free to contact us when you have any problems before or after purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lovely, yet time consuming!
reviews.reviewText: These stands are incredibly sturdy and offer amenities I need in a moments notice while lounging about. Having outlets built in is also a plus, especially as a techie. I really do love these stands, BUT! You will need time to build them. There are a lot of small parts, and multiple tools needed to put it all together. Give yourself time and patience, and follow the guide as closely as possible. Definitely not confusing, just a lot of things to accomplish between each step. Overall, I’m satisfied.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars I adore this table, but it really is not the easiest to build.
reviews.reviewText: I struggled with building this table, even with my fair share of doing projects like this in the past. This took the cake. That aside, I really love the quality and the LED strip as well--although, it does come off here and there. So far, it seems to have been sticking to where it should be. But, I do love the color options, and overall, I enjoy using it to store some small paintings and other little things that normally would be ruined by my pesky cats if left out. Very sturdy, holds up well, and so far regarding utility, no complaints!
